Prequisites
===========

--PDT--

./configure -ICPC -prefix=${PDT_INSTALL_LOCATION}
make 
make install

--TAU--
./configure -c++=icpc -pdt_c++=icpc -prefix$={TAU_INSTALL_LOCATION} -pdt=${PDT_INSTALL_LOCATION}
make install

gzip
====

1. First do the configure under gzip-1.6/instrumented with optional prefix. (./configure CC=icc -prefix=${GZIP_INSTALL_LOCATION})
2. Then do a make inside gzip-1.6 (This step is required other wise there will be errors in the next step)
3. Now run gzip-1.6/instrument.sh
4. Now do a second make with instrumented files.
5. make install

